        <div class="youtube-video">
          <div class="youtube-video__video">
            <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_mMGcl7J8v0">Watch our video about Pension Wise appointments</a>
          </div>
          <div class="youtube-video__transcript">
            <p>
              <a href="#main-transcript" class="visually-hidden js-video-transcript-toggle" aria-controls="main-transcript">Show video transcript</a>
            </p>
            <div class="video-transcript js-video-transcript" id="main-transcript" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true">
              <noscript class="js-video-transcript-copy">
                <p>When I retire I hope to travel. Maybe move house.</p>
                <p>I wasn't sure how to deal with the financial planning side.</p>
                <p>That’s why I needed to try to clear the mist and get something sorted really.</p>
                <p>I have about four pension pots. To be honest I was quite confused.</p>
                <p>There's different types and I had more than one type of pension. I wanted guidance.</p>
                <p>I made an appointment with Pension Wise. Saw a guider there. The appointment was free.</p>
                <p>It lasted about forty-five minutes.</p>
                <p>She guided me through what the options were and made it clear to me what I can and can’t do with my pension.</p>
                <p>The guidance I received was excellent.</p>
                <p>I really now feeling control of my financial matters. It really, really was good.</p>
              </noscript>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h2 class="landing-subheading">Book a free appointment</h2>
        <p>Find out about how you can take your pension money, from getting a regular income to taking your whole pot as cash.</p>
        <p>Speak to us over the phone or in person somewhere local to you.</p>
        <p>Pension Wise is free and impartial – we don’t recommend products or companies and won’t tell you how to invest your money.</p>
        <p><a href="/appointments" class="button">Book a free appointment</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
